<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٢٠- عَبد الرَّحمَن بْن عُبَيد.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ عليا، رَضِيَ الله عنه، قَولَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال قَنان بْن عَبد اللهِ النَّهمِيّ:</span> شَيخٌ مِنَ الحَيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الكُوفيّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>